This project was made for the course CAI (Conception d’Applications Interactives: Design of Interactive Applications)
by Jeronimo Perez and Mía Torres López

For the control of Pan and Tilt of a camera, close distance (Bluetooth) or Far distance (SMS)

-Bluetooth (Chat - Client/Server)
-SMS
-SharedPrefences (storing data)
-Accelerometer
-Joystick
-Change between activities
